data.title: Ground Forces of Ukraine
data.meta_description: Unit list of Ukrainian Ground forces, the land troops of Ukrainian Army and its main combat power.
data.text: Ukrainian Ground forces are the land forces of Ukrainian Army and its main combat power. The land forces consist of numerous independent tank, mechanized and artillery units, but also Army aviation and Air Defense. The main task of the ground forces is the protection of Ukrainian land, repelling enemy attacks and breaking through the enemys defenses.
